high_descs: Turn left and walk to the wall then turn left and walk to the stool.
Pick up the ice cream scoop that's in front of you near the loaf of bread.
Take a big step to your left then walk to the stove.
Put the scoop in the pan on the back right burner.
Pick up the pan on the back right burner.
Turn left and walk to the counter.
Put the pan to the left of the egg that's in front of you.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with an ice cream scoop in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the wall, then turn left to face the counter.
Pick up the large spoon from the counter.
Turn left and move forward, then turn right and go to the stove.
Put the large spoon on the pan, on the right side of the stove.
Pick up the pan with the large spoon on it.
Turn left and go straight ahead to the counter.
Place the pan on the back of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a large spoon in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left then head to the island
Pick up the ladle on the island
Turn left then go to the stove
Put the ladle on the pan at the stove
Pick up the pan with ladle
Turn left then walk toward the counter
Put the pan with ladle on top of the counter beside the egg
anns.task_desc: Put the pan with ladle on the counter
